data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Spacious 1,701 sqft 3 Bedroom/2 Bathroom, 1995 DOUBLE-WIDE mobile home in INDIAN OAK Community. OPEN FLOOR PLAN with Living Room, Dining Room, PLUS Den.  The home is on .63 of an acre with NO BACKYARD NEIGHBORS. Nestled along the wooded Alafia River Reserve. No flood insurance is required (Flood Zone X). SPLIT-STYLE Master BEDROOM with an en-suite Master BATHROOM that has a garden tub with a separate shower.  Two other bedrooms share the second bathroom on the other side of the home. KITCHEN has wood cabinets with a tiled backsplash and the appliances are from 2020. Carpet and laminate flooring were replaced in 2020. A sliding glass door leads to the backyard. The LAUNDRY nook includes a WASHER/DRYER. Public water with septic tank. A very low HOA ($150 year). Indian Oak is a quiet community with one road leading in and out with easy access to State Road 60. A must-see!
